Overview
========

Postgis documentation is written in docbook xml.
Input file is postgis.xml. From that file we can
convert to chunked html, single file html and pdf.

Rules are:

	make html/postgis.html
	make chuncked-html
	make postgis.pdf

Common requirements
===================

debian packages:
	- xlstproc 

Requirements to build postgis.pdf
=================================

debian packages:
	- passivetex 
	- xmltex 
